Bottomline Paymode-XPaymode-X is the largest and fastest-growing B2B electronic payment network, processing over $200 billion per year to more than 365,000 member organizations. Payers and Vendors harness the power of this innovative, cloud-based solution to simplify the migration to electronic payments. Paymode-X is quickly becoming the means by which businesses prefer to pay and get paid.
Watch VideoPaymode-X with Visa Payables Solutions






Contact Us 



 
Anchor: Overview
OverviewPaymode-X couples powerful technology with industry-leading client services. Organizations move from paper to electronic payments much more quickly than an in-house ACH program allows. Streamlined implementation and Paymode-X's Intelligent Engagement methodology drive fast go-live and highly effective Vendor enrollment.Payers enjoy the convenience of secure electronic payments and earn valuable rebates on their Accounts Payable spend.Vendors appreciate faster direct deposit payments, detailed remittance and user-friendly online access to information that helps them forecast receivables. Payers and Vendors share access to secure, instant and downloadable transaction information, minimizing phone inquiries and manual data entry.To reduce administrative burden and allow members to focus on running their businesses, the Paymode-X Member Services team handles Vendor bank authentication, Notices of Change / payment returns and support inquiries.MORE DETAILS ON PAYMODE-X



Anchor: Resources











Video
Vendors Connect Payments Faster with Paymode-X










White Paper
Not Your Average ACH: 4 Reasons to Consider a Payments Network










eBook
How Paymode-X Helped 3 Organizations Reduce Costs, Earn Rebates and Boost Efficiency









Anchor: Benefits


Benefits & Features


 
Electronic payments lower check and bank costs, mitigate fraud risk and create efficiencies.Payment scheduling tools optimize working capital and allow control over payment timing.Robust remittance improves performance and assists in audits.Electronic payments and remittance eliminate manual processes, freeing resources to focus on strategic, value-add activities.

Dedicated Vendor Advocate teams customize outreach on behalf of Payers to deliver maximum Vendor value and speedy enrollment.Multi-step Vendor authentication process validates member bank and account information -- ensuring the security of all trading partnerships.Experienced Member Services team supports Payers and Vendors.Cloud-based delivery provides real-time access to product and feature updates.

 

