CareersInnovate, win, and grow with Bottomline.





Contact Us 




 
Anchor: Careers
Careers at BottomlineBottomline Technologies is an energetic, growing, exciting company—and it's a great place to learn and grow your career.
Bottomline has been at the forefront of business payment automation for 30 years, starting as a small team launching a check printing solution from a little office in Exeter, NH. Today, we’re a public company with more than 1,600 employees, helping thousands of companies in 92 countries make their complex business payments simple, secure and streamlined.Will you be part of our ongoing revolution? Search Jobs






Anchor: People & Culture



People and Culture 

People Make Us GreatFor every individual in this organization, everything we do is 
focused on customer delight. Whether you are a human resources 
specialist, software developer, or sales person, we understand 
that everything we do connects back to the customer, helping them grow 
their business and win in their markets. Our goal is to ensure customer 
success, and in turn, ensure our success.We share ideas, innovate together, and support each other personally 
and professionally. By working collaboratively with customers, partners,
 and colleagues, we achieve our common goal of exceeding customer 
expectations.

Anchor: College Hire



College Hire &
Apprentices 

College Hire ProgramBottomline’s College Hire Program is designed to identify, train, and promote the organization’s next generation of business leaders.Each new hire class begins their Bottomline experience with a comprehensive, four to six week cross-functional training curriculum. This provides a team-based, “behind the scenes look” at what puts Bottomline in Business NH Magazine’s “Best Companies to Work For” Hall of Fame. Our unique approach allows new hires to gain a holistic understanding of the entire business before taking on their assigned roles, while providing each candidate with the foundation necessary to develop a successful career at Bottomline.APPLY NOW



 
Guiding Principles

Everything we do every day is based on our Guiding Principles:


Delight Customers!
Innovate, communicate, win, and grow.
Work with and for each other.
Do the right thing.
Create and grow sustained business value.
Be a company of which all can be proud.



Grow and Win in Your CareerWe are proud to work at Bottomline. We feel good about the work we do and how we help our customers. If you want to help us build on our success, check our current US employment opportunities.Bottomline Technologies is an Equal Opportunity and Affirmative Action Employer participating in the Employment Verification (E-Verify) program.




